attributionInfo.brokerName: Mossy Oak Properties of the He

data.description:
Fall in Love with This Cozy Ranch Home on Spacious Acreage! Step into a home adorned with the warmth of Cherry Oak. The entrance, living room, kitchen, and dining area are graced with beautiful Cherry Oak paneling. Imagine walking on possible Cherry Oak hardwood floors throughout the main floor, perfect for cozy autumn nights. The owner believes that underneath the carpeted areas, you might uncover these same exquisite Cherry Oak floors.
For those who love to tinker, there are 2 propane furnaces in the 4-car shop area and a convenient half bath. This setup is a car enthusiast's dream, with space for remodeling and crafting your automotive dreams.
Acreage and Beyond:
But the magic doesn't stop there! This property boasts great acreage, including an impressive 80 x 42 barn  If you're interested, now is the perfect time to consider purchasing the adjacent property, which is also on the market. It offers 7.47 acres and features a 3+/- acre stocked lake – a serene oasis for fishing and relaxation. This opportunity would allow you to have a total of 20+/- acres, perfect for embracing the full beauty of the fall season. Acreage to be verified by the buyer. 
Don't let this fall season slip away without making this charming property your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and start your journey to an idyllic autumn retreat in Liberty, MO.
